                                "type": "text",
                                "text": "\n\nagain, ohmjs gives you parse tree (how is this not AST?), and if expression is deeply nested enough, your \"say, 128KB\" would go bye bye too.\nPlease, show a concrete (pseudocode) example of an AST."
                            }
