        "type": "message",
        "ts": "1760420519.741269",
        "client_msg_id": "6AD32C2C-B77E-46F5-A681-218DC08F7B94",
        "text": "Oh and bots. I think linen uses a bot. It's wild that \"bots\" exist, and predate LLMs, in this enterprise product. What a weird thing, Slack is.",
        "team": "T5TCAFTA9",
        "user_team": "T5TCAFTA9",
